Viveka Davis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Viveka_Davis 0 Viveka Davis (born August 19, 1969) is an American actress who has starred in television series and films. As a young actress, she was best known for her role in the 1983 NBC TV miniseries V as Polly Maxwell, a role she reprised in the 1984 sequel V The Final Battle.
